Genre 
<taxonomicName id="4C326DC91A4CFFD3D34F0FA2FDB2F962" authority="Karsch, 1891" authorityName="Karsch" authorityYear="1891" box="[278,545,1739,1764]" class="Insecta" family="Acrididae" genus="Badistica" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="329" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B946CA581A4CFFD3D34F0FA2FE04F964" bold="true" box="[278,407,1739,1762]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="329">BADISTICA</emphasis>
Karsch,1891
</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B8D164A1A4CFFD2D2950E67FDCBFE0D" blockId="18.[173,1406,1806,1863]" lastBlockId="19.[211,1444,301,395]" lastPageId="19" lastPageNumber="330" pageId="18" pageNumber="329">
Genre forestier ouest-africain (de la 
<collectingCountry id="F32556DA1A4CFFD3D0090E67FD40F8A3" box="[592,723,1806,1829]" name="Sierra Leone" pageId="18" pageNumber="329">Sierra Leone</collectingCountry>
au 
<collectingCountry id="F32556DA1A4CFFD3D1580E67FCE2F8A3" box="[769,881,1806,1829]" name="Cameroon" pageId="18" pageNumber="329">Cameroun</collectingCountry>
), comprenant 6 espèces microptères dont 3 sont présentes au Nimba, faciles à distinguer d’après leur système de coloration: 
<taxonomicName id="4C326DC91A4CFFD3D1E50E59FB86F8C1" authorityName="I. Bolivar" authorityYear="1905" box="[956,1045,1840,1863]" class="Insecta" family="Acrididae" genus="Badistica" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="329" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ornata">
<emphasis id="B946CA581A4CFFD3D1E50E59FB86F8C1" box="[956,1045,1840,1863]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="329">B. ornata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
a le dessus du pronotum noir avec 2 ou 3 taches médianes jaunes, tandis que les deux autres espèces ont le dessus du pronotum vert ou verdâtre uniforme; les fémurs postérieurs sont de la même couleur, assombris à l’apex chez 
<taxonomicName id="4C326DC91A4DFFD2D1EE0838FBB7FEEE" authorityName="Ramme" authorityYear="1929" box="[951,1060,337,360]" class="Insecta" family="Acrididae" genus="Badistica" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="330" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="simpsoni">
<emphasis id="B946CA581A4DFFD2D1EE0838FBB7FEEE" box="[951,1060,337,360]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="330">B. simpsoni</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, alors que ceux de 
<taxonomicName id="4C326DC91A4DFFD2D6B20838FADDFEEE" authorityName="Chopard" authorityYear="1958" box="[1259,1358,337,360]" class="Insecta" family="Acrididae" genus="Badistica" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="330" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fascipes">
<emphasis id="B946CA581A4DFFD2D6B20838FADDFEEE" box="[1259,1358,337,360]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="330">B. fascipes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
ont une coloration très tranchée jaune et noir.
</paragraph>
